name: Nonreporting; penalty
text: Any person subject to section 350-1.1(a) who knowingly prevents another person from reporting, or who knowingly fails to provide information as required by section 350-1.1(c) or (d), shall be guilty of a petty misdemeanor. [L 1985, c 17, §3; am L 1987, c 204, §5 and c 339, §4]
